":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43679,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/14\/prophet-always-with-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":7240,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: The Prophet always with Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 14, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: Umar was placed upon his bier as the people surrounded him, supplicated for him, and performed the funeral prayer over him before he was taken away. I was there, and nothing else held my attention but a man putting his hand on my shoulder. It was Ali,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6674,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/19\/bilal-from-slave-to-master\/","url_meta":{"origin":7240,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Freedom: Bilal, from our slave to our master","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 19, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, used to say, \u201cAbu Bakr is our master and he emancipated our master,\u201d meaning Bilal. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3754 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u0646 \u062c\u0627\u0628\u0631 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f\u00a0\u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u064a\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0648 \u0628\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0633\u064e\u064a\u0650\u0651\u062f\u064f\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0648\u064e\u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0642\u064